7. Open Xcode and select your project. Go to Product > Archive to archive your project.

8. Sign in with your Apple ID and click Submit to submit your app to the App Store.

9. In the App Store Connect web interface, go to your app and select Prepare for Submission. Upload your archive that you created in Xcode.

10. Select Distribution as the App Review Information and choose TestFlight as the App Delivery Method. Enter the email addresses of the users you want to invite to the beta testing program.

11. Click Save and wait for the app review process to complete. Once it's approved, your app will be available in TestFlight for your testers to download and test.

